snippet.title: TaxiOfTheAsteroids
snippet.description:
Un jeu gratuit crée à l'occasion de la Game Jam Francophone 8. Le jeu s'inspire du jeu Asteroids but in this game you shoot at asteroids to find a way to drive you clients safely.

=== Links ===
 - Download this game on itch :  https://takeru-grima.itch.io/taxi-of-the-asteroids
 - Discover my other games : https://takeru-grima.itch.io/
 - Game FR 8 : https://itch.io/jam/game-jam-francophone-episode-8
